      "properties": {
        "text": "LTX-Video 2.3 — First-Last Frame to Video (FLF2V)\n\nMODEL: ltx-video-2b-0.9.7.safetensors\n  HuggingFace: Lightricks/LTX-Video\n  ComfyUI node pack: ltxvideo (Kosinkadink)\n\nSETUP:\n1. first_frame.png = your starting pose/scene\n2. last_frame.png  = your ending pose/scene\n3. Both images auto-resize to 768x512\n4. 97 frames @ 25fps = ~3.9 second output\n\nDIGITAL-STUD USE CASES:\n- Pose A -> Pose B transition (character animation)\n- Scene morph / background transition\n- Outfit change (same character, different clothes)\n- Expression change (neutral -> smiling/angry)\n\nFLF2V MODE: pins first+last frames in latent space\nSTG guider improves temporal consistency\nCFG=3.0 optimal for FLF2V (lower than I2V)\n\nVRAM GUIDE:\n  RTX 3090/4090 24GB: fp8 + tiled VAE\n  RTX 5090 32GB: fp16, no tiling\n  Enable collapsed nodes below for fp8\n\nEXTEND: add ControlNet OpenPose before\nLTXVImageToVideo to lock body skeleton\nSee pose_controlnet.json for setup"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "note"
      ]
    },
